  message: <<EOM
Users running Solaar need to be in the solaar group to read and write from the Logitech receiver.

A devd rule has been added to added to make the necessary changes.
Restart devd for these changes to take effect immediately.

# service devd restart

Add users to the solaar group to grant them access.

# pw groupmod solaar -m your_user

Then log the user out and back in again for the changes to take effect.

EOM
}
